# ==========================================
# CoinTrack - Docker Ignore Rules
# Purpose: Prevent sensitive/huge files from entering build context
# ==========================================

# 1. Build Artifacts
**/target/
**/build/
**/*.class

# 2. IDE & Git Metadata
**/.git/
**/.idea/
**/.vscode/
**/*.iml
.classpath
.project
.settings

# 3. Logs & Temp Files
**/logs/
**/*.log
**/*.tmp

# 4. Sensitive Files
**/.env
**/.env.*
**/secrets/

# 5. OS Metadata
**/.DS_Store
**/Thumbs.db

# 6. Docker itself (avoid recursion)
**/docker/
!docker/Dockerfile
